      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with full regression test suite and documented build environment required at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "Solver is version-controlled but regression test suite covers only 40% of critical code paths; build environment documentation is incomplete. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
