      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy verification using manufactured solutions on at least three mesh refinement levels required.",
      "rationale": "Only two mesh refinement levels were tested; manufactured solution approach was applied to simplified 2D geometry rather than the full 3D impeller geometry. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
    },
