      "acceptanceCriteria": "Richardson extrapolation-based GCI reported for all QoIs with GCI < 5% required.",
      "rationale": "GCI was computed for pressure rise but not for hemolysis index directly. Hemolysis discretization error estimated indirectly via surrogate. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
    },
    {
