      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments must span the full COU operating envelope including maximum design speed.",
      "rationale": "Validation data available only up to 3000 RPM; COU operating envelope extends to 4000 RPM. Extrapolation beyond validated range not supported. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
