      "acceptanceCriteria": "All material properties and boundary conditions must have documented uncertainty distributions for Monte Carlo propagation.",
      "rationale": "Blood viscosity and density distributions assumed Newtonian with fixed values; non-Newtonian effects and hematocrit variability not included in UQ. Flagged as epistemic gap. Achieved level 1 against required level 4."
    },
