      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental sample size must support statistical confidence intervals on measured hemolysis index.",
      "rationale": "Experimental dataset contains n=3 replicates per operating point; insufficient for robust confidence interval estimation at MRL 5. Flagged as epistemic gap. Achieved level 1 against required level 3."
